<div class="section sWhat" id="what" align="center">
  <h1>What is Bitcoin?</h1>
  <h3 class="header-info-block">Bitcoin is a new class of <strong class="title">digital money</strong><br>
    that allows you to send and recieve payments from person to person<br>
    <strong class="title has-tooltip" title="send money to anywhere in the world and the receiver can start using it after only 10 minutes">very fast</strong><br>
    without any intermediate agent (bank or corporation)<br>
    <strong class="title has-tooltip" title="5 cents of dollar to send 10,000 USD anywhere">at almost zero cost</strong></h3>
  <div class="flex-video video-container" align="center">
    <iframe width="560" height="315" src="https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/Um63OQz3bjo?rel=0&cc_load_policy=1" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>
  </div>
  <div class="show-for-medium-up" id="footsteps" align="right">
    <%= image_tag "footsteps.png", id: "footsteps-image", width: "174", height: "444" %>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="section sStart" id="start" ng-controller="DemoCtrl">
  <button class="radius round large super-button" id="show-demo" ng-click="showDemo()">Start using Bitcoin <i class="fi-bitcoin bitcoin-button"></i></button>
</div>

<div class="section sUse" id="use">
  <h1 id="fourth">What can I do with Bitcoin?</h1>
  <p>Today it's possible to pay almost everything you can pay with old currencies with Bitcoin like: ...</p>
